{"tid":682477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]摩天輪車廂突然翻轉　1死6傷畫面曝光","createTime":"2018-05-29T02:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T02:24:31.000Z","uid":72478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d91b752a9e849faa1290ef48911694f6782cadd","tid":682477,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x3YP9KU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fx3YP9KU.jpg&h=f509b729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度阿納恩塔普爾（Anantapur）一處遊樂園發生驚悚摩天輪意外。其中一車廂在運轉中翻覆，多名乘客直接被拋飛到半空中，造成一名10歲女童死亡，其餘6人受重傷。據悉，摩天輪操作人員當時處酒醉狀態，才會無法即時阻止憾事發生，事後被當地民眾痛毆一頓。<br />\n<br />\n綜合印度媒體報導，這起事件發生在當地時間27日晚間，事發摩天輪其中一個車廂的螺栓鬆動，導致車廂整個從摩天輪上掉落。目擊者說，事發前就有人發現其中一車廂不穩定，立刻提醒操作人員，但該名操作人員卻醉倒了，無法及時應變。<br />\n<br />\n從網傳影片中可見，摩天輪當時運轉速度不慢，其中一個半開放式車廂明顯失去平衡傾覆，導致車廂內多位遊客跌落。報導指出，傷者都被緊急送往醫院治療，其中一名10歲女童阿姆拉莎（Amrutha）傷重不治。報導指出，酒醉的操作員遭憤怒民眾毆打，目前已經被警方帶回調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gK6Rzcs1zyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgK6Rzcs1zyQ&d=Am5SbhvUSQ1Wlx40sPgUt8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=e3be8cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gK6Rzcs1zyQ</a>"},{"pid":"c6308d8ea66a1fb6357ad818a7e490c09374b0c9","tid":682477,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1aed45291090b445e21af52f4704b601932026","tid":682477,"uid":170044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線國家 痴撚線民族<br />\n飲醉酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d6a299aeaf0bdd7c293bcba9687563df16ea6f","tid":682477,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"事後被當地民眾痛毆一頓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9199c9ab19515529179eb69bbbc4f444e6355022","tid":682477,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"無敵風火輪"},{"pid":"1be536bceb5e51367c7e4eb8a1bb65f2c805a3d9","tid":682477,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"點解會郁得咁快？<br />\n平時d摩天輪好慢嫁喎"},{"pid":"9c60b87be68d36e259db86d43091ebae2b1fc58b","tid":682477,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:19:55.000Z","msg":"轉得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa90420096803e8e820d879955fd95587415a35","tid":682477,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"係咪咁快...<br />\n就算有人為失誤<br />\n個輪設計本身有問題。<br />\n冇理由唔限速。"}]}